<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٥٦٧٠ -<span class="c5"> ابْنُ يَمَانٍ عَنْ سُفْيَانَ قَالَ:</span> لَا يَفْقَهُ عَبْدٌ حَتَّى يَعُدَّ الْبَلَاءَ نِعْمَةً وَالرَّخَاءَ مُصِيبَةً<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>